{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_02_02",
  "title": "miho 2話 ⅢXの休日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（その後も、何ヶ所かを回って）\n（ⅢXのライブツアーは満員御礼のうちに終了した）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（ After that‚ the IIIX live tour continued through）\n（ several locations and ended with full houses everywhere.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（厳しい日程の中で頑張ってくれた三人には）\n（長めにオフを取って、英気を養ってもらうつもりだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Planning on giving the three who worked hard through）\n（the tough schedule a good long break to recharge their batteries.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6433.333333299998,
          "startTime": 17.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 16.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、{user}さん\n今日もお仕事ですか、お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ if it isn't {user}-san.\nWorking hard again today‚ I see. Much appreciated.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8158996418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それ俺の台詞ですからね！？\nスリクスのみなさんは、今日からオフのはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nah‚ that's my line to you‚ ain't it?!\nIIIX folks are supposed to be on break starting today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、kanaはここぞとばかりに\n旅行に出かけたみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ kana seized the moment to\nhead off on a trip‚ it seems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "さっきSNSを見たら\n観光名所で自撮り写真を上げていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just saw it on social media a while ago‚\nshe's been posting selfies at tourist spots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "franはあちこち電話をしてましたし、ファッション\n業界のイベントにでも行くつもりなんですかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And fran's been on the phone non-stop‚ maybe she's\nplanning to attend some fashion industry event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0413042614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……あの子達\n出先でまた馬鹿なことをやっていないといいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… those kids‚\nHopefully‚ they ain't causing trouble out there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……\nmihoさんも、ゆっくりしたらいいのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha…\nYou should take it easy too‚ miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "時間もあることですし、動画でも観ようと思ったんです\n事務所の方が、音響がいいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got some time on my hands‚ so I thought I'd watch some videos.\nThe office has better sound quality‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2480171614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その映像、今度ライブバトルするグループですよね\nただの対戦相手の研究じゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That video‚ it's of the group we'll be battling in the live battle next time‚ ain't it?\nJust doing some research on our competition!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……何よ、アイドルに休みなんかないと思え\nなんて言ったのは、どこの誰だったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What's this‚ thinking an idol doesn't get any breaks?\nI wonder who was it that said such a thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ……もしかして\nこの間俺が言ったこと、気にしてます……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… could it be\nYou're bothered by something I said the other day…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "気にしてなんかいません\n泥酔した私が軽率でした、申し訳ありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not bothered at all.\nI was just out of line when I was drunk‚ I apologize.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "私の休日なのだから、私がどう使おうと自由でしょう\n言われなくとも、休むべき時にはちゃんと休みます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my day off‚ after all‚ I'm free to use it as I please.\nI'll take a rest without being told‚ when it's time to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、お願いしますよ\nくれぐれも無茶はしないで下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ please do.\nAnd take care not to overdo it‚ alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "studio",
      "startTime": 97.5545216878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（書類を片付けてたら、もうこんな時間だ）\n（……あれ、スタジオにまだ誰か残ってるのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was sorting out paperwork and now it's gotten this late.）\n（…Huh‚ someone's still at the studio?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……あら、{user}さん\nこんな遅くまで、お仕事お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ {user}-\nYou're still working hard at this late hour‚ kudos to ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それは俺の台詞ですって！　……この前\n言ったこと、やっぱり気にしてますよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nah‚ that's my line to you! …About the other day\nYou're still hung up about what I said‚ ain't you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4443700154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "別に、気にしてなんかいませんってば",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the umpteenth time‚ I ain't concerned about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "必要ならちゃんと休みますよ\n今は、そこまで必要ないというだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll take a break if I need one‚ sure as shootin'.\nRight now‚ I just don't need one is all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4443700154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "私、確かにこの事務所では最年長ですけど\nでも、まだ疲れを引きずるような歳じゃありませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ I might be the eldest in this office\nBut I ain't at the age where I carry tiredness with me yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "ダラダラしていたら、それだけ体が鈍ってしまいます\nコンディションを戻すの大変なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I laze around‚ my body will just get sluggish.\nIt's darn tough getting back in condition.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.4777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "それに……あいにく、私は凡人なので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus… unluckily‚ I'm no prodigy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "……franとkanaは身体能力が高いですし\n飲み込みも凄く早いですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…fran and kana‚ they have high physical capabilities‚\nAnd they catch on mighty quick‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "残念ながら、私はそこまでではないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sadly‚ I can't quite keep up with that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、mihoさんだって\nずっと、あの二人と一緒にやってきたんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But‚ miho‚ you've\nbeen keeping pace with those two all this time‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "――ええ。だって私、それだけ練習してきましたから\nだから練習をサボって、体を鈍らせたくはないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Yep. 'Cause I practiced just as hard.\nThat's why I can't afford to skimp on practice and let myself get out of shape.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルのトップが遠のきますし――\nfranとkanaに追い抜かれるなんて腹が立つもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd be drifting away from being a top idol then—\nAnd the thought of fran and kana overtaking me just sticks in my craw.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4269587199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（……プライドと意識の高さはさすがだな）\n（けど、あまり根を詰め過ぎるのもなぁ……それに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Gotta admit‚ her pride and awareness are top-notch.）\n（But overdoing it ain't wise neither… Plus‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.2110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "でも俺は、例の酔っ払った後のステージも\n観てて、本当に楽しかったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was there for that stage after the night she had a few too many‚\nand I genuinely had a great time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.7443700154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時の？\nそりゃ、目立ったミスはありませんでしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You talking about that time?\nWell‚ there weren't any glaring mistakes‚ sure‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.1110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "録画を見返してみたら\nやっぱり二日酔いのせいで、動きが甘かったですし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but looking back at the recording‚\nthe hangover did make my moves a bit soft…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.9110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "完成度という意味ではそうなんでしょうけど\nいい意味で気が抜けて、気楽に観られるというか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In terms of perfection‚ I reckon that's true‚\nbut it sort of felt more relaxed in a good way‚ easy to watch‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.1110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "それ、褒めてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that… supposed to be a compliment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "褒めてますよ。これをうまいこと打ち出せたら\nスリクスの新たな魅力になるとも思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure is. If we can market that just right‚\nI figure it could be a new charm point for IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.9777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、星見プロでは\n観客とアイドルの距離が近いですものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ at Hoshimi Pro.\nThe distance btween the audience and the idols sure is close‚ ain't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.3110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk024.m4a",
      "text": "親しみやすさを演出したいということなら\n……まぁ、理解は出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If y'all are aiming to give off a more approachable vibe…\n…well‚ I get where you're coming from.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.2777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。ですから、肩の力の抜き方も\n少し覚えてみるっていうのは、どうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. So‚ how about learning\nhow to relax your shoulders a little bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.3443700155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk025.m4a",
      "text": "……と、言われても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even if you say that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.3443700154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk026.m4a",
      "text": "私、高校の頃に養成所に入ってから\n土日はほぼそちらでレッスンしてましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ever since I started at the training school in high school‚\nI pretty much spent all my weekends taking lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.3443700155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk027.m4a",
      "text": "デビューしてからはずっと仕事でしたし\n一日休みが入っても、家事をしていれば終わりますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And after I debuted‚ it's been work non-stop.\nEven if I get a day off‚ it's over by the time I finish up with chores.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.1777033488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_02_02-mhk028.m4a",
      "text": "……今更、お休みをいただいたところで\n何をしたらいいのか、分からないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So honestly‚ if I took some time off now‚\nI wouldn't even know what to do with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.3110366821,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}